Do to overwhelming OOC e-mails, the council (KSLawdogg, Inferno731, Yanshosh, 
and former member JP3884) have decided to regulate these e-mails. I will send 
a formal write up of this rule soon. Part of this rule will be no advertising 
another RPG over our RPG if you wish to do so do it on the MESSAGE BOARD. We 
have one.
